Package: wpm
Type: Package
Title: Well Plate Maker
Version: 1.1.2
Authors@R: c(person('Helene', 'Borges', role = c('aut', 'cre'), 
                    email = 'borges.helene.sophie@gmail.com'),
            person('Thomas', 'Burger', role = 'aut',
                    email = 'thomas.burger@cea.fr'))
Description: This is a shiny application for creating well-plate plans. 
    It uses a backtracking-inspired algorithm to place samples on plates 
    based on specific neighborhood constraints.
